[[!table  data="""
URL                                         | Author (Year)        | N  | Subject Selection | Duration  | Diets Compared | Most Interesting Outcome (causal proximity to QALYs, magnitude, p-value)
<https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26003334/> | Pastore et al (2015) | 20 | Hypercholesterol  | 4 mo each | AHA & Paleo    | Weight: AHA: -1.9kg, Paleo: -9.3kg (p<0.001). TC, LDL, TG all decreased and HDL increased much more on Paleo (all p<0.001)
